/public/docs/attribute/ALLOW_DUAL_WIELD

Format: (Living_Object)->set_attribute("ALLOW_DUAL_WIELD", iValue);

Description:
  The ALLOW_DUAL_WIELD will allow the Living_Object to
  dual wield weapons. It won't change any other restrictions
  beyond letting those that normally can't dual wield to
  be able to dual wield. The iValue is only used to turn
  the attribute on or off.
